#: ../../agents.rst:104
msgid "ReAct 工具循环"
msgstr "ReAct Tool Loop"

#: ../../agents.rst:106
msgid ""
"``PersonAgent.step()`` / ``ask()`` 的核心是基类提供的 "
"``run_react_loop``：每轮让模型提交一个结构化 工具决策，运行时校验、执行并把结果写回上下文，循环直至 ``finish`` "
"或回合上限。这把 LLM 的自由生成 限制在可审计的工具结果里，也方便 replay 复盘。"
msgstr ""
"The core of ``PersonAgent.step()`` is a decision-execution-feedback loop."
" In each round, the model submits only one structured ``ToolDecision``; "
"the runtime validates it, executes it, and writes the result back into "
"context. This design constrains free-form LLM generation to auditable "
"tool results and also makes replay analysis easier when reviewing why "
"each step happened."

