msgstr ""
"``config.json`` is static. ``AGENT.json`` is written back by "
"``persist_agent_json`` (which calls ``build_agent_json``) during "
"``to_workspace`` and acts as the agent's self-description snapshot. "
"Thread and tool logs live under ``.runtime/logs/``."

